This folder is reserved for the necessary publication of the databases to the client. Without this, the data would only be viewable on the server side.

'this.userId' is used quite often, since that is a very convenient feature of Meteor.js

'Roles.userIsInRole' is used to detect if the current user is of an admin status. For example, Roles.userIsInRole(this.userId, 'site') checks to see if the current user is a site coordinator.